hadiths[38]{hadithnumber,text}:
3041,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main mominon ka unke nafson se bhi ziyada haqdaar hun, jo shakhs faut ho jaey aur is par qarz ho aur usney qarz ki adaegi ke liye koi chiz bhi na chhodi ho to uski adaegi merey zimmey hai aur jisney koi maal chhoda ho to wo uskey warison ka hai.'' aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''jo shakhs qarz ya pasmandagaan chhod jaey to wo merey paas ayen main unka haami aur madadgar hun.'' aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''jisney maal chhoda to uskey warison ke liye hai aur jo shakhs bojh (yani qarz ya aulad) chhod jaey to wo hamari taraf ayen.'' muttafaq aleh."
3042,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''muqarrara hissey unke mustahiqeen (haqdaar) ko do aur jo baqi bachey wo (maiyat ke) qarib tareen mard (rishtey daar) ka hissa hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3043,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''musalman kafir ka, aur kafir musalman ka waris nahin ho sakta.'' muttafaq aleh."
3044,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qom ka azad karda ghulam unhi mein se hota hai.'' Bukhari."
3045,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qom ka bhaanjaa unhi mein shumar hota hai.'' muttafaq aleh. ( وَذْکِرَ حَدِیثُ عَائِشَۃَ : ( اِنَّمَا الْوَلَاءُ . . . . .) ( فِیْ بَابِ قَبْلَ بَابِ السَّلَمِ وَ سَنَذْکُرُ حَدِیْثَ الْبَرَاءِ : ( الْخَالَۃُ بِمَنْزِلَۃِ الْاُمِّ ( فِیْ بَابِ بُلُوْعِ الصَّغِیْرِ وَ حَضَانَتِہِ اِنْ شَاءَ اللہُ تَعَالیٰ) Aaisha (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ( اِنَّمَا الْوَلَاءُ . . . . .) ) باب السلم  se pehley baab (silsile) mein zikr ho chuki hai, aur Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''khaala, maa ke maqam par hoti hai.'' ham (باب بلوغ الصغیر و حضانتہ) mein Insha Allah Taala zikr karengey."
3046,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''do mukhtalif Deen ke hamil afrad baham (aapas mein) waris nahin ho saktey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
3047,Hazrat Imam Tirmizi ne usey Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Tirmizi.
3048,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qatil (maqtool ka ( waris nahin ho sakta.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
3049,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (maiyat ki) maa na honey ki surat mein daadi, nani ke liye chata hissey muqarrar farmaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3050,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : jab bachcha paidaish ke waqt aawaz nikaley (cheekhey aur phir faut ho jaey) to uski Namaze-janaza padhi jaeygi aur uski virasat bhi taqseem hogi.'' rawahu ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
3051,"Hazrat Kasir bin Abdullah apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qom ka azad karda ghulam unhin mein se hai, qom ka haleef (dost) unhi mein se hai aur qom ka bhaanjaa unhi mein se hai.'' rawahu Darmi ."
3052,"Hazrat Miqdam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main her momin se khud us se bhi ziyada talluq rakhta hun, jo shakhs qarz ya pasmandagan chhod jaey to unka khayal rakhna hamari zimme-daari hai, aur jo shakhs maal chhod jaey to wo uskey warison ke liye hai. aur jis ka koi maula (himayati aur madadgar) na ho. uska main maula hun, uskey maal ka main waris banunga, uskey qaidi ko mein chhudaaoonga, jis ka koi waris na ho uska waris mamu hai, wo uskey maal ka waris hoga aur uskey qaidi ko chhudaaeyga.'' aur eik riwayat mein hai : ''jis ka koi waris na ho uska main waris hun, uski taraf se diyat bhi dunga aur uska waris bhi banunga, aur jis ka koi waris na ho uska mamu waris hai, wo uski taraf se diyat dega aur uska waris baneyga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3053,"Hazrat Waasila bin Isqaa' (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aurat teen wiraasatein pa sakti hai, apney azad kiye huey ghulam ki, apney paaley huey bachchey ki aur apney us bachchey ki jiskey mutalliq usney liaan kiya ho.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
3054,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne kisi azad ya ghulam aurat se zina kiya, (aur bachcha paida hua) to wo bachcha, zina se paida hua hai, wo (apney zaani baap ka ( waris hoga na uska baap uska waris hoga.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
3055,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka azad karda ghulam faut ho gaya, aur usney kuchh maal chhoda, aur usney koi qaribi rishte-daar chhoda na aulad, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''uski meeras uski basti ke kisi aadmi ko dey do.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Tirmizi."
3056,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, khuza'aa qabiley ka eik aadmi faut ho gaya to uski meeras Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh ki gaee. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''uska koi waris ya koi rishte-daar talash karo.'' unhoney uska koi waris paya na koi rishte-daar, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : khuza'aa qabiley ke kisi umr raseeda shakhs ko dey do.'' Abu-Dawud, aur Abu-Dawood hi ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''khuza'aa qabiley ka koi bada aadmi dekho.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3057,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, tum ye aayat tilawat kartey ho : '' wasiyat puri karney ke baad jo tum wasiyat kartey ho ya qarz ki adaegi ke baad.'' be-shak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qarz ko wasiyat se pehley ada karney ka faisla farmaya, aur sagey bhai waris hotey hain, soteley bhai waris nahin hotey, aadmi apney sagey bhai ka waris hoga soteley bhai ka waris nahin hoga.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja. aur Darmi ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''sagey bhai (eik hi maa ki aulad) waris hongey aur mukhtalif maaon ki aulad (yani soteley bhai) waris nahin hongey.'' rawahu Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
3058,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Saad bin Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) ki ehliya Saad bin Rabeea se apni dono betiyan lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai to arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! ye dono Saad bin Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) ki betiyan hain, unka walid ghazwae-uhad mein aap ke sath shareek ho kar Shahid ho gaya. in dono ke chacha ne unka maal ley liya hai aur unke liye koi maal nahin chhoda, agar maal hoga to inki shaadi ho jaeygi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''iskey mutalliq Allah faisla farmaeyga.'' isliye aayate meeras nazil hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke chacha ko pegham bheja ke Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ki dono betiyon ko do tihai do aur un dono ki walida ko aathwan hissey do, aur jo baqi bachey wo tumhara hai.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, ibne-Maja. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
3059,"Hazrat Huzail bin Shurehbil bayan kartey hain, Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) se beti, poti aur behan ke hissey ke barey mein sawal kiya gaya to unhoney farmaya : beti ke liye nisf (aadha), behan ke liye nisf(aadha), aur tum ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas jaao wo bhi merey muwaafiq fatwa dengey , Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se masla puchha gaya aur unhen bataya gaya ke Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye fatwa diya hai, to unhoney farmaya : tab to main gumrah ho gaya, aur main hidayat-yafta logon mein se nahin hun, main iskey mutalliq wohi faisla karunga jo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kiya tha, beti ke liye nisf (aadha), poti ke liye chata hissey isi tarah do tihai mukammal hua aur jo baqi bachey wo behan ke liye hai, ham Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaye to unhen ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke fatwa ke barey mein bataya to unhoney farmaya : jab tak ye allaama tum mein mojud hai mujh se masla na puchha karo. Bukhari."
3060,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kiya, mera pota faut ho gaya hai, uski meeras mein mera kitna hissey hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tumharey liye chata hissey hai.'' jab wo wapis muda to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey bulaya aur farmaya : ''tumharey liye eik aur chata hissey hai.'' jab wo wapis muda to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey bulaya aur farmaya : ''doosra chata hissey (ziyada haq-daar na honey ki wajeh sey) tumharey liye rizq hai.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
3061,"Hazrat Qabisa bin Zuwaib bayan kartey hain, daadi , nani , Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aai aur usney apni meeras ke barey mein aap se masla daryaft kiya, to unhoney us se kaha : tumharey liye Allah ki kitab mein koi hissa hai na Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat mein , aap jaeyn yahan tak ke main logon se poochhlun : unhoney puchha to Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir tha ke aapney usey (yani daadi / nani ko) chata hissey diya, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : kya tumharey sath koi aur bhi hai? to Muhammad bin Muslima ne bhi wesay hi kaha jaisey Mughira ne kaha tha, to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne us (daadi / nani) ke mutalliq usey nafiz kar diya, phir eik aur daadi/nani umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aai aur apni meeras ke mutalliq daryaft kiya, to unhoney farmaya : wo chata hissey hi hai, agar tum dono ikhatti hon to wo tum dono ke darmiyan taqseem hoga, aur tum dono mein se jo bhi akeli hogi to wo hissey usey milega.'' rawahu Malik, Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, Darmi aur ibne-Maja."
3062,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) us daadi ke barey mein jisey apney bete ke sath hissey mila, farmaya : wo pehli daadi hai jisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bete ki mojudgi mein chata hissey ata kiya jabkey uska beta zinda tha. Tirmizi, Darmi. Imam Tirmizi ne isey zaeef qarar diya hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur Darmi."
3063,"Hazrat Suhak bin Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke naam khat likha ke Ashyam Zababi ki ehliya ko uskey khawind ki diyat se meeras do.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
3064,"Hazrat Tameem daari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha ke ehle shirk mein se us aadmi ke barey mein , jo kisi musalman shakhs ke haathon par Islam qubul kar ley, sharae hukm kiya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo uski hayaat aur maut ke barey mein tamam logon se ziyada haq daar hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
3065,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi faut ho gaya to usney sirf eik ghulam chhoda jis ko usney azad kiya tha Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya uska koi waris hai? '' Sahaba ne arz kiya : nahin, sirf wo eik ghulam hai jisey usney azad kiya tha, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski meeras usko dey di. rawahu Abu-Dawood, Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
3066,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo maal ka waris ho sakta hai wo wala ka waris hoga.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : is hadees ki sanad qawi nahin. rawahu Tirmizi."
3067,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo meeras daure-jahiliyat mein taqseem ki gaee to wo jahiliyat ki taqseem ke mutabiq hai, aur jo meeras daure-Islam mein hui to wo Islam ki taqseem ke mutabiq hai.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
3068,Hazrat Muhammad bin Abi Bakr bin Hazam (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney apney walid se kaee martaba suna wo kaha kartey they : umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) phuphi ke mutalliq tajjub se kaha kartey they ke bhatija to uska waris banta hai jabkey wo uski waris nahin banti. rawahu Malik.
3069,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : faraaiz (meeras ka ilm) seekho. aur ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne itna izafa kiya, Talaq aur Haj (ke mutalliq bhi seekho) un dono ne kaha : kyonkey ye tumharey aham deeni umur (baton) mein se hain. rawahu Darmi."
3070,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo musalman wasiyat karna chahta hai uskey liye munasib nahin ke wo do raaten bhi yun guzar dey ke wasiyat uskey paas likhi hui na ho.'' muttafaq aleh."
3071,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Fateh Makka ke saal mein shadeed bimar ho gaya yahan tak ke main maut ke kinarey pahunch gaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) meri iyaadat ke liye tashrif laye to maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! merey paas maal bahut ziyada hai. aur meri sirf eik beti uski waris hai, kya main apney sarey maal ke mutalliq wasiyat kar dun? farmaya : ''nahin.'' maine arz kiya, apney maal ka do-tihai? farmaya : ''nahin.'' maine arz kiya : nisf (aadha)? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin.'' maine arz kiya, tihai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tihai, jabkey tihai bhi ziyada hai, agar tum apney warison ko maal-daar chhodo ye us se behtar hai ke wo tang dast hon aur logon ke aagey haath phelatey phiren. aur tum Allah ki raza ke liye jo bhi kharch karogey is par tumhen ajr diya jaeyga, yahan tak ke wo luqma jo tum apni ehliya ke munh tak pahunchatey ho.'' muttafaq aleh."
3072,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main mareez tha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne meri iyaadat ki, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne wasiyat ki hai? ''maine arz kya : ji haan , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kitney maal ki?'' maine arz kiya : Allah ki raah mein apney sarey maal ki, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne apni aulad ke liye kya chhoda hai? ''maine arz kiya : wo kafi maal daar hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''daswin hissey ki wasiyat kar.'' main israr karta raha, yahan tak ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hukm diya : '' tihai ki wasiyat kar, jabkey tihai bhi ziyada hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
3073,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khutba Hajjatul-wadaa ke moqe par farmatey huey suna : ''Allah ne her haq daar ko uska haq dey diya, waris ke liye wasiyat karney ka koi haq nahin.'' Abu-Dawud, ibne-Maja. aur Imam Tirmizi ne ye izafa naqal kiya : ''bachcha biwi ke Malik ka hai jabkey zaani ke liye pathar (yani rajm) hai, aur unka hisab Allah ke zimme hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood, ibne-Maja aur Tirmizi."
3074,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki sanad se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se marwi (bayan) hai aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''waris ko wasiyat ka haq nahin illa ye ke waris chahen.'' ye riwayat munqata' hai. ye Masaabeh ke alfaz hain, aur Daarqutni ki riwayat mein hai : ''waris ke liye wasiyat karna jayez nahin, magar ye ke uske waris chahen.'' rawahu Dar-Qutni."
3075,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak aadmi aur aurat saath saal tak Allah ki itaat mein nek amal kartey rehtey hain, phir unhen maut aati hai to wo wasiyat mein kisi ko nuqsan pahuncha jatey hain, to un dono ke liye jahannam ki aag wajib ho jati hai.'' phir Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''virasat ki taqseem wasiyat ke laagu aur qarz ki adaegi ke baad hai aur wo wasiyat nuqsan pahunchaney wali na ho. . . . aur ye bahut badi kamiyabi hai.'' rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
3076,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs wasiyat par faut hua to wo sidhi raah aur sunnat par faut hua , wo itaat guzari aur shahadat par faut hua , aur wo us haal mein faut hua ke uski maghfirat kar di gaee.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
3077,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Aas bin Waael ne wasiyat ki ke uski taraf se sau ghulam azad kiye jaeyn , unke bete Hisham ne unki taraf se pachas ghulam azad kiye , aur unke bete Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unki taraf se pachas ghulam azad karney ka irada kiya to kaha : yahan tak ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla daryaft kar lun , wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! merey walid ne wasiyat ki thi ke unki taraf se sau ghulam azad kiye jaeyn , Hisham ne unki taraf se pachas azad kar diye hain aur baqi pachas reh gaey hain, kya main unki taraf se azad kar dun? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar wo musalman martaa to tum uski taraf se ghulam azad kartey, ya tum uski taraf se sadqa kartey ya tum uski taraf se Haj kartey to uska usey sawab pahunchta.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3078,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne apney waris ki meeras kaati to roze-qiyamat Allah Taala uski jannat ki meeras kaat dega.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
